      "title": "British Prime Minister Boris Johnson resigns",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to reports, British Prime Minister Boris Johnson is going to resign as the leader of the Conservative Party today.",
        "The Conservative Party leadership election is coming soon. The new prime minister will take office before the party conference in October.",
        "2 ministers and officials recently resigned from Boris Johnson's cabinet.",
        "In this case, Boris Johnson is going to step down as party leader. (R)"
